<bibRefCitation id="EF864B31FF81FFA599B0F8B5F81E3764" author="Castro, J. I." box="[461,607,1863,1889]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" pagination="1 - 10" refId="ref268612" refString="Castro, J. I. (2011) Resurrection of the name Carcharhinus cerdale, a species different from Carcharhinus porosus. Aqua, International Journal of Ichthyology, 17, 1 - 10." type="journal article" year="2011">Castro 2011</bibRefCitation>
